Category 7: The End of the World (2005)

Dutch
In dit vervolg van "Category 6: Day of Destruction" wordt de storm steeds sterker en
blijkt het de grootste storm van de Verenigde Staten te zijn. Judith Carr bereidt
zich hier op voor, terwijl Tommy Tornado juist op de storm afgaat, gesteund door
Faith Clavell. In de tussentijd beweren dominee Donny Hall en zijn vrouw Penny dat
deze storm een bijbelse plaag is. De mensen realiseren dat het niet lang meer duurt
voordat deze storm Amerika vernietigt.

Englisch
A series of devastating storms are leveling major cities across the globe, and it's
up to discredited scientist Faith Clavell (Shannon Doherty), dedicated storm chaser
Tommy Tornado (Randy Quaid), and the FEMA head Judith Carr (Gina Gerson) to journey
into the eye of the storm and find out just why mother nature has turned so violently
on mankind in the shocking sequel to 2004's weather-gone-wild thriller Category 6: Day
of Destruction. An unprecedented Category Six storm has leveled the Eiffel Tower and
reduced the Great Pyramids to rubble, and as the pitch black funnel clouds lay waste
to anything and everything in their path, three dedicated heroes attempt to discover
whether the malevolent weather is the cause of global warming, or something far more
sinister. When a vengeful gang of terrorists threaten to use the storms to their
advantage by staging a large scale attack the likes of which the world has never seen,
it seems as if it very well may be the end of the world.
